Definition:

Second term: tally
Positive Examples.explanation: It is True since "forth" has the opposite meaning to that of "tally".

Negative Examples.input:

Second term: look up
Negative Examples.explanation: It is False since "pray" does not have the opposite meaning to that of "look up". Hence, output "Yes" is incorrect.

Negative Examples.input:

Second term: flat land
